definitions.definition: Of the order Osmeriformes of ray-finned fish , characterised by having the maxilla in the gape of the mouth, radii absent from the scales , and loss of the basisphenoid and orbitosphenoid bones .

main_definition: Of the order Osmeriformes of ray-finned fish , characterised by having the maxilla in the gape of the mouth, radii absent from the scales , and loss of the basisphenoid and orbitosphenoid bones .
